---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Utilifyer"
  description="Privacy Policy for Utilifyer.com. Learn how we handle your data and protect your privacy."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8">Last updated: April 24, 2025</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">1. Overview</h2>
        <p>Utilifyer.com ("we", "our", or "us") is a collection of free online tools. We are committed to protecting your privacy. This policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p><strong>We do not collect any personal information.</strong> All tools on Utilifyer.com run entirely in your browser. Data you enter into any tool (text, numbers, files) is never transmitted to our servers — it stays on your device and is discarded when you close or refresh the page.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">We may collect anonymous, aggregated usage data through third-party analytics services (see Section 4) such as:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on pages</li>
          <li>General geographic region (country/region level)</li>
          <li>Browser type and operating system</li>
          <li>Referring website</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">This data cannot be used to identify you personally.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">3. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We may use cookies and similar technologies to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Remember your preferences</li>
          <li>Enable advertising served by Google AdSense</li>
          <li>Collect anonymous analytics data via Google Analytics</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time. Some features may not function correctly without cookies.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services that may set their own cookies or collect data:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — displays advertisements. Google may use cookies to serve ads based on your interests. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — collects anonymous traffic statistics. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — provides CDN and hosting infrastructure. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">You can opt out of Google's personalized advertising at <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">adssettings.google.com</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">5. Data Security</h2>
        <p>Since all tool processing happens client-side in your browser and we do not store personal data, there is minimal data security risk. Standard HTTPS encryption is used for all connections to our site.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">6. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>Our website is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any information from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided personal information through our site, please contact us and we will promptly address it.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Since we do not collect personal data, there is generally no personal data to access, correct, or delete. For any concerns about data collected by third-party services, please refer to their respective privacy policies and opt-out tools.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page will reflect any changes. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">9. Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please <a href="/contact" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">contact us</a>.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
